《'''急诊室'''》（{{lang-en|'''Casualty'''}}，風格化：'''Casual<sup>+</sup>y'''）是一部英国醫療劇，由{{link-en|傑瑞米·布洛克|Jeremy Brock}}和{{link-en|保羅·昂溫|Paul Unwin}}创建，原監製為{{link-en|傑蘭特·莫利斯|Geraint Morris}}<ref>{{cite news |author1=Anthony Hayward |title=Obituary: Geraint Morris |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/obituary-geraint-morris-1250780.html |accessdate=2019-11-17 |work=[[獨立報|獨立報]] |date=1997-07-15 |language=en |archive-date=2017-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171031022153/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/obituary-geraint-morris-1250780.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，自1986年9月6日每周六晚開始于[[英國廣播公司第一台|英國廣播公司第一台]]上播出<ref name="DVD Times">{{cite web|url=http://www.dvdtimes.co.uk/content.php?contentid=61214|title=Casualty: Series 1|publisher=DVD Times|accessdate=2012-03-25|language=en|archive-date=2014-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202180510/http://www.dvdtimes.co.uk/content.php?contentid=61214|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是世界上最长寿的醫療劇<ref name="longest">{{cite web | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/drama/casualty/20years/video/ | title = Longest Running Emergency Medical Drama | format = Flash | work = 急诊室官网 | language = en | access-date = 2012-02-03 | archive-date = 2016-02-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160202131434/http://www.bbc.co.uk/drama/casualty/20years/video/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。該劇情節設定在虚构的{{link-en|霍爾比市醫院|Holby City Hospital}}，围绕着医院[[急症室|急症室]]里的医生和病人。該劇的衍生節目《[[霍爾比市|霍爾比市]]》于1999年开始播放，场景亦设定在同一间医院<ref>{{cite book|last=Gibbs|first=Nicholas|title=Writing Television Drama: Get Your Scripts Commissioned, Teach Yourself |language=en}}</ref>。两部劇集的情节和演员不时会有关聯，但两部劇集可以单独收看。

為慶祝《急诊室》播放30週年，其於2016年8月27日系列第31的第1集，播出一集長篇劇集，以作記念。而該系列的最後一集，其创建者保羅·昂溫特別回来，並以一台攝影機，五個吊桿操作員，四十個麥克風，進行一鏡過的拍攝制作工作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://metro.co.uk/2017/07/29/casualty-to-broadcast-special-one-take-episode-for-tonights-series-finale-6815443/|title=Casualty to broadcast special ‘one take’ episode for tonight’s series finale|date=2017-07-29|publisher=Joe Gamp|language=en|accessdate=2019-11-17|archive-date=2017-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170730021431/http://metro.co.uk/2017/07/29/casualty-to-broadcast-special-one-take-episode-for-tonights-series-finale-6815443/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

