=== 拍攝 ===
《急诊室》醫院早期取景於[[西南英格蘭|西南英格蘭]]的{{link-en|布里斯托城市学院|City of Bristol College}}。到系列第26的第16集為止，節目主要拍攝取景于布里斯托市中心附近<ref>{{cite news |author1=Alexei Sayle |title=Alexei Sayle: I'd love to live in Holby City – nothing like the real world |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/voices/commentators/alexei-sayle-id-love-to-live-in-holby-city-nothing-like-the-real-world-9242781.html |accessdate=2019-11-17 |work=[[獨立報|獨立報]] |date=2001-08-21 |language=en |archive-date=2019-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191117055549/https://www.independent.co.uk/voices/commentators/alexei-sayle-id-love-to-live-in-holby-city-nothing-like-the-real-world-9242781.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，{{link-en|布里斯托港|Bristol Harbour}}及[[克利夫頓吊橋|克利夫頓吊橋]]等當地著名地標，亦曾出現於劇中<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0096555/locations|title=Filming locations|work=[[IMDb|IMDb]]|accessdate=2019-11-17|language=en|archive-date=2015-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150504083708/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0096555/locations|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而在之後劇集轉至位於[[南威爾斯|南威爾斯]][[卡迪夫|卡迪夫]]的{{link-en|Roath Lock}}（英國廣播公司其中一間電視製作工作室）進行拍攝<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/pressreleases/stories/2009/03_march/26/casualty.shtml |title=Press Office — BBC confirms Casualty move from Bristol to Cardiff area |publisher=BBC |date= |accessdate=2019-11-17 |language=en |archive-date=2011-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110421101716/http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/pressreleases/stories/2009/03_march/26/casualty.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://roathlock.com/index.php/casualty|title=Roath Lock Studios – Casualty|publisher=BBC Wales|accessdate=2011-09-12 |dead-url=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110911210943/http://www.roathlock.com/index.php/casualty|archivedate=2011-09-11 |language=en}}</ref>。在[[卡迪夫|卡迪夫]]拍攝的第一集，即系列第26的第17集，因記念劇集播放25週年以及其搬遷，而播出一集80分鐘的長篇劇集<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.atvtoday.co.uk/first-cardiff-produced-casualty-episode-to-air-in-january-2/ |title=First Cardiff produced Casualty episode to air in January |author1=Doug Lambert |date=2011-12-13 |work=ATV Today |accessdate=2019-11-17 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190902155034/https://www.atvtoday.co.uk/first-cardiff-produced-casualty-episode-to-air-in-january-2/ |archive-date=2019-09-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

